Introduction


CHECKMATE was a four-member co-ed group under GRACE COMPANY Entertainment. They debuted on September 21, 2020 with the single album "Drum". On December 18, CHECKMATE's YouTube channel creator and manager announced that CHECKMATE had disbanded, with the members pursuing individual activities.
